者的渴求多是抽象的“位置”，而非具体的人；当上位者变弱，无法承担欲望和权力的秩序时，关系会失衡\n4. 坏倾向的涌现：当情与欲无法精确切割时，自私、占有欲、嫉妒心、破坏欲等爱情里的坏倾向会浮出水面，过往稳定的权力结构、游戏结构彻底坍塌","type":1},{"desc":"・情欲关系的权力结构难以维持源于情感与欲望的不可分割","detail":"1. 权力结构的本质：欲望的游戏本质是权力的游戏，若情与欲彼此交织、情感表露，权力结构会随之坍塌\n2. 人的需求矛盾：即使是看似无懈可击的女神、男神、支配者或上位者，也需要温暖和忠诚的拥抱，想要不计后果的狂热真挚爱情\n3. 维持的难度：需要极高的智慧才能维持情欲的权力结构，普通人难以做到全身而退","type":1}]},{"desc":"结语","timestamp":237000,"detail":"","points":[]}],"chapter_recommend_type":1,"chapter_abstract":"SM游戏中可能会发现爱情，但这种爱情往往伴随着痛苦和危险。游戏会放大人性弱点，让人在情感和欲望上产生混淆。当情感和欲望交织时，权力结构会崩溃，导致各种坏倾向浮出水面。要在情和欲之间维持精确的分离，才能守护现有的权利结构和游戏方式。","chapter_recommend_source":2,"push_scene":[],"chapter_bar_color":null},"ad_charge_passive_unlock_config":{"trial_btn_config":{"btn_show_second":3,"btn_text":"秒后解锁本集","btn_show_frequency":1,"show_second_type":2},"broadcast_btn_config":{"btn_show_second":5,"btn_text":"秒后解锁下一集","btn_show_frequency":1,"show_second_type":2}},"common_button":{"button_list":[{"basic_info":{"btn_name":"playlet_iaa_next","exemptions":[1,2],"btn_type":"entertainment","btn_ui_style":0,"buttons":[{"content":{"content":""},"click_action":{"click_action":1,"btn_data_Keys":null,"behavior_type":0},"btn_data_keys":null}],"btn_datas":null},"priority":200400}]},"trends_infos":null,"chapter_bar_color":null,"flash_mob_trends":0},{"aweme_id":"7609672430625344783","desc":"人，没法得到自己觉得不配的事物 #认知 #独立思考 #两性关系","create_time":1771765707,"author":{"uid":"3749764821694632","card_entries_not_display":null,"nickname":"狐狸的观念","personal_tag_list":null,"can_set_geofencing":null,"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/aweme-avatar/tos-cn-i-0813_owCnIA2ADGjAQeeglS3AhVCbhvY9CkA34IAnsX","url_list":["https://p3-pc.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/aweme-avatar/tos-cn-i-0813_owCnIA2ADGjAQeeglS3AhVCbhvY9CkA34IAnsX.jpeg?from=327834062"],"width":720,"height":720},"creator_tag_list":null,"risk_notice_text":"","follow_status":1,"data_label_list":null,"story25_comment":0,"not_seen_item_id_list_v2":null,"custom_verify":"","ban_user_functions":null,"cf_list":null,"interest_tags":null,"private_rela